    {
      "Text": "Security update for webkit2gtk3",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for webkit2gtk3 fixes the following issues:\n\nUpdate to version 2.46.3 (bsc#1232747):\n\n- CVE-2024-44244: Processing maliciously crafted web content may lead to an unexpected process crash.\n- CVE-2024-44296: Processing maliciously crafted web content may prevent Content Security Policy from being enforced.\n\nNew references to version 2.46.0 (boo#1231039):\n\n- CVE-2024-44185: Processing maliciously crafted web content may lead to an unexpected process crash.\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
